Package com.whitespike.vision

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseSensesToHigherSenses
    Service method that generates higher senses from base senses passed in.
    BlobEdgeFromBlob
    Service method that extracts a blob edge from a blob and adds it to the blob.
    BlobToSense
    Service method that turns a blob into a sense.
    BufferedImageToBlobsInParallel
    Service method to extract blobs from bufferedimage using parallel processing.
    BufferedImageToBlobsInParallel.BlobParallelCombiner
    Used when combining row blobs into their larger forms using parallel processing.
    BufferedImageToBlobsInParallel.BlobParallelFinder
    Used when finding blobs from a row using parallel processing.
    ChangedPixelsFromOldEnv
    Used to find and contain the pixels that changed between two images (previous visual input vs current visual input).
    ChangedPixelsFromOldEnv.junctionList  
    ChangedPixelsToBlobs
    Service method that takes in the changed pixels and turns them into blobs.
    ChangedPixelsToBlobs.ChangedPixelsBlobParallelFinder  
    ComparisonScoreBasedOnOrientation
    Compares two senses, returns a score based on how likely they are to be the same sense.
    IdentifyPixelChange
    Service method that turns a list of PixelPosChanges (literal changes) into a list of PixelChanges (Ex: RightTurn, RightDownDiagonal, etc.).
    ImaginaryHigherSensesFromSenses
    Service method that extracts imaginary senses from base/higher senses.
    OrientationFromHigherSenseComponents
    Service method that creates an orientation object for a higher sense based on its components.
    OverallPixelChangesFromPixelChanges
    Service method that creates a list of PixelOverallChanges from a list of PixelChanges.
    RawEnvToAbstractEnv
    Service method that creates an abstract env from a raw env.
    RemoveOldSensesFromEnv
    Service method that removes all old (no longer existing) senses from an env while updating it.
    SenseCombiner
    Service method that combines a list of senses into an existing list of senses (merging when appropriate).
    SenseCombiner.SenseParallelCombiner  
    SenseCombinerBlobEdgeFromBlob
    Altered get blob edge from blob code for use in the sense combining process (for performance reasons).
    SenseCombinerBlobToSense
    The sense combiner version of blob to sense (for performance reasons).
    SenseToHigherSense
    Service method to extract higher senses from currentSenseIn.
    UpdateEnv
    Service method to update an env to the current instance of time.
    UpdateSenses
    Service method to update an env's senses using the newly discovered senses.
